article.description: Sandy Cohen III had 20 points, 10 rebounds and eight assists as Green Bay routed Florida International 98-68 in the CIT second round on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Cohen scores 20 to lead Green Bay past FIU 98-68 in CIT
article.linkText: Cohen scores 20 to lead Green Bay past FIU 98-68 in CIT
article.story: GREEN BAY, Wis. -- Sandy Cohen III had 20 points, 10 rebounds and eight assists as Green Bay routed Florida International 98-68 in the CIT second round on Tuesday night. Cohen made 8 of 10 foul shots. JayQuan McCloud had 17 points and five assists for Green Bay (19-16). Tank Hemphill added 12 points and nine rebounds. Manny Patterson had 10 points and eight rebounds for the hosts. Green Bay scored 53 first-half points after scoring 59 in the first 20 minutes of a 102-94 victory over East Tennessee State in the first round. Devon Andrews had 15 points for the Panthers (20-14), which finished the season tied for the second-most wins in program history. Trejon Jacob added 13 points.
